Instruction

1)read the KUWAIT AIP FILE : start with your dep or arr process, if arriving look for STAR and arriving via KUA01/02 to rw15R/L 33R/L and if departing use departing via 15R/L 33R/L to KUA01/02 and then look for one of the SIDS available, continue flight planning using the ATS ROUTES SECTION which will guide you to the next FIR(no ATS ROUTES FOR ASVIR KUNRU AS THEY ARE SID/STARS).                                            
2)CHART(1) contains RW TO KUA01/02 & SID/STAR for RALKA ALVAX SESRU BOXIK DEBTI ASVIR KUNRU KFR OKKK CHART(2) contains RW TO KUA01/02 & SID/STARS for BONIM BUBER available in KML format.
3)can be used for all flight simulators, load the kml files into google my maps or QGIS  to view coordinates.
